        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2843274049" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10754617438308953362">Such an awesome treat for people who have read Allison&apos;s work before (if you haven&apos;t read Bastard Out of Carolina - stop what you&apos;re doing, and go read it!). It offers a lot of context, I think, for her novels. But also - what a beautiful writer. And I&apos;ll never not love the centering of relationships between women. Read this book in one sitting on a plane. </span>
